title: 10 minutes daily
info:
10 minutes only to Irancell for 1 day  For the price of 65 Afghani. 
Press the green button to activate and the red button to deactivate. 
Send U to 303 to activate ID and to deactivate

title: 20 minutes weekly
info:
20 minutes only to Irancell for 7 days at the price of 130 Afghanis.   
Press the green button to activate and press the red button to deactivate. 
Send IW to 303 to activate and U to deactivate

title: 40 minutes monthly
info:
40 minutes only to Irancell for 30 days at the price of 260 Afghanis. 
To activate, press the green button  And press the red button to deactivate. 
To activate IM and to deactivate send U to 303
